Read `AGENTS.md` first. Then read `AI_ASSISTANTS.md`, `.ai/README.md`, and the
matching `.ai/assistant/flows/*.flow.md` for the task.

For Alatyr help or aliases (`alatyr-ai-inventory`, `alatyr-adaptation`,
`alatyr-add-ai`), read `.ai/assistant/help.md` and
`.ai/assistant/flows/operation-routing.flow.md`.

This Cursor rule is a bridge, not the source of truth.
